nodes.name: Thiamin-triphosphate phosphohydrolase
nodes.rxn: Thiamin triphosphate + H2O <=> Thiamin diphosphate + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: ADP:thiamin-diphosphate phosphotransferase
nodes.rxn: Thiamin diphosphate + ADP <=> Thiamin triphosphate + AMP

nodes.name: Thiamin diphosphate phosphohydrolase
nodes.rxn: Thiamin diphosphate + H2O <=> Thiamin monophosphate + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: ATP:thiamin-phosphate phosphotransferase
nodes.rxn: ATP + Thiamin monophosphate <=> ADP + Thiamin diphosphate

nodes.name: 1-deoxy-D-xylulose 5-phosphate:thiol sulfurtransferase
nodes.rxn: 1-Deoxy-D-xylulose 5-phosphate + Iminoglycine + Thiocarboxy-[sulfur-carrier protein] <=> 2-[(2R,5Z)-2-Carboxy-4-methylthiazol-5(2H)-ylidene]ethyl phosphate + Sulfur-carrier protein + 2 H2O

nodes.name: [enzyme]-S-sulfanyl-L-cysteine:adenylyl-[sulfur-carrier protein] sulfurtransferase
nodes.rxn: [Enzyme]-S-sulfanylcysteine + Adenylyl-[sulfur-carrier protein] + Reduced acceptor <=> AMP + Thiocarboxy-[sulfur-carrier protein] + [Enzyme]-cysteine + Acceptor

nodes.name: ATP:[sulfur-carrier protein] adenylyltransferase
nodes.rxn: Sulfur-carrier protein + ATP <=> Adenylyl-[sulfur-carrier protein] + Diphosphate

nodes.name: L-tyrosine 4-methylphenol-lyase (2-iminoacetate-forming)
nodes.rxn: L-Tyrosine + S-Adenosyl-L-methionine + Reduced acceptor <=> Iminoglycine + 4-Cresol + 5'-Deoxyadenosine + L-Methionine + Acceptor

nodes.name: 5-amino-1-(5-phospho-D-ribosyl)imidazole formate-lyase (decarboxylating, 4-amino-2-methyl-5-phosphomethylpyrimidine-forming)
nodes.rxn: Aminoimidazole ribotide + S-Adenosyl-L-methionine <=> 4-Amino-2-methyl-5-(phosphooxymethyl)pyrimidine + 5'-Deoxyadenosine + L-Methionine + Formate + CO

nodes.name: 2-methyl-4-amino-5-hydroxymethylpyrimidine-diphosphate:2-(2-carboxy-4-methylthiazol-5-yl)ethyl phosphate 2-methyl-4-aminopyrimidine-5-methenyltransferase
nodes.rxn: 4-Amino-5-hydroxymethyl-2-methylpyrimidine diphosphate + 2-(2-Carboxy-4-methylthiazol-5-yl)ethyl phosphate <=> Thiamin monophosphate + Diphosphate + CO2

nodes.name: Thiamin diphosphate phosphohydrolase
nodes.rxn: Thiamin diphosphate + H2O <=> Thiamin monophosphate + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: NAD+:glycine ADP-D-ribosyltransferase (sulfide-adding)
nodes.rxn: NAD+ + Glycine + Hydrogen sulfide <=> Nicotinamide + ADP-5-ethyl-4-methylthiazole-2-carboxylate + 3 H2O
